PROPERTY_DATA.VALUE: Ben and Jerry's Sweet Cream & Cookies

TEXT_DATA.TEXT: This is the CON spec for BEN & JERRY'S AMET Sweet Cream & Cookies Fair Trade non-GMO 458mL for AMET countries.
Statement of Identity: Sweet Cream Ice Cream with Chocolate Sandwich Cookies (12%)

Ingredients: Cream, Concentrated Skim Milk, Liquid Sugar, Water, Sugar, Wheat Flour, Egg Yolk, Vegetable Oil, Cocoa , Salt, Raising Agent (Sodium Bicarbonate), Natural Flavour and Flavourings, Emulsifier (Soybean Lecithin), Thickeners (Guar Gum, Carrageenan)
Contains milk, wheat, egg and soybean
Made on equipment that also makes products which contain peanuts and tree nuts.
